american frank reed 57 who was held hostage for 42 months by a 
group calling itself the organization of islamic dawn 
president bush has publicly thanked iran and syria for helping 
secure their freedom bush has said the united states could try to 
help determine the fate of the four missing iranians 
israeli officials reiterated that they are not opposed to a 
prisoner swap in principle but stressed that an exchange should 
