fears during a speech to the final session of the congress 
we will continue with all force the fight against rightwing 
extremism and antisemitism interior minister wolgang schaeuble 
said 
before the ceremony bronfman and other leaders of the 
organization toured the inside of the villa 
they stood in what is known as the fireplace room the room 
that historians say is most likely the one used for the conference 
there nazi ss boss reinhard heydrich and his coconspirators 
planned the final solution the extermination of european jews 
its just absolutely mindboggling when you hear that 
heydrich wanted to come here to a secluded spot because he wasnt 
sure his colleagues would go along with him said bronfman he 
he was so happy they did he took a glass of brandy and had a 
cigar what kind of people were these 
later congress leaders traveled to east berlin for a meeting 
with prime minister lothar de maiziere 
there has never been a germany without jews de maiziere 
told the jewish delegation there can only be a germany with 
jews or there wont be any germany 
the democratically elected east german government in a dramatic 
gesture last month accepted joint responsibility for the 
holocaust for more than four decades the nowousted communist 
authorities had denied any responsibility 
