arsenal against israel in case of an israeli attack 
at the time of the joint usbritish customs sting operation in 
march iraq said the devices described by us prosecutors as 
nuclear warhead detonation capacitors allegedly being smuggled to 
baghdad were intended for a nonnuclear university laser project 
the 40 capacitors seized in march were labeled as air 
conditioning units in an effort to get around us bans on export 
of militarily sensitive technology us officials said 
three people were arrested in england in connection with the 
case after an 18month investigation by us and british customs 
officials 
capacitors can be used to create the first electrical spark in 
the chain reaction that leads to a nuclear explosion 
