the move followed renewed us threats to cut off all funding to 
who if its 167nation assembly approved the application by the 
palestine liberation organization such a move would boost the 
plos campaign for international recognition of its state 
the state department maintains the plo is not entitled to full 
membership in any un organization because it does not meet 
internationally recognized criteria of statehood including control 
of territory 
we should use political means to attain health objectives but 
not health issues to serve political ends nakajima told 
