even longer delay truly said two shuttles already are in the 
hangar atlantis and the newly returned discovery and work on 
them would be disrupted he said 
its hard for me to speculate because i dont know if we have 
to change anything truly said but he added well think a 
long time before we decide not to fix it on the pad 
the valve in question in one of columbias two freon cooling 
loops controls the proportion and rate of freon distributed 
between the crew cabin heat exchanger and the cooling system for 
payloads 
engineers on sunday saw an unexplained change in the flow of 
coolant nasa said 
