injuring two of five astronauts 
the simulated problems included main engine shutdown less than 
two minutes into the flight a leaking power unit inability to 
purge the shuttles hydrogen lines and excessive winds such 
failures when combined are extremely unlikely lenoir said 
truly said a series of simulated shuttle accidents are planned 
to make sure the communications loops are in place 
an accident on board an orbiting shuttle will be simulated at 
johnson space center in houston around late june followed by a 
mock crash landing at edwards air force base calif in august 
