imports from south korea after receiving a complaint from an 
industry group 
the antidumping complaint was brought by the association for 
legalauto radio measures comprised of major european 
manufacturers philips nv grundig ag and blaupunktwerke gmbh 
the group which makes more than 70 percent of ecmade car 
radios said that by forcing ec car radio prices down the south 
korean exporters had caused considerable profit cuts and job cuts 
among ec manufacturers 
