most of the assets are in arkansas he said 
atlantic richfield co will buy 175 working natural gas wells in 
southwestern oklahoma said earl sims a spokesman for atlantic 
richfields energy division atlantic richfield said the wells 
produce 14 million cubic feet of natural gas daily 
sims wouldnt disclose what atlantic richfield would pay for the 
wells but the difference between usxs total sale price and what 
sonat said it would pay is 53 million 
officials at both sonat and atlantic richfield said they would 
not operate the usx properties as joint ventures 
pittsburghbased usx said it expects to complete the sale in 
from two to three months 
texas oil amp gas co the usx division that owns the properties 
accounted for about 55 percent of the companys 1989 sales 
usxs sale announcement comes a day after shareholders voted on 
new york financier carl c icahns proposed splitting of the 
corporations steel division and energy holdings including texas 
oil amp gas 
